{"tid":944114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2小野豬大埔道覓食　慘死車輪下","createTime":"2018-12-17T02:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T02:43:27.000Z","uid":41404,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"53906c1c0c72e37546129a63f17b781892b2f3ac","tid":944114,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181217/photo/bkn-20181217064110479-1217_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181217084151\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181217%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181217064110479-1217_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181217084151&h=e4f9a85f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n野豬被撞後傷重死亡。(葉嘉文攝)<br />\n<br />\n長沙灣發生野豬落山搵食遭撞斃意外，今日(17日)清晨6時許，一頭小野豬在大埔道近金山郊野公園一帶沿馬路旁覓食，期間姓郭(56歲)男子駕駛一輛電單車正往沙田方向行駛，至近金山路時，小野豬突然走出，郭疑收掣不及，將小野豬撞倒，小野豬當場倒地奄奄一息，而郭亦翻車倒地受傷，他自行報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員其後接報到場，郭因腳部受傷，由救護車送院治理，警員檢查證實小野豬已傷重死亡，並發現附近約15米外有另一隻野豬屍體，懷疑亦於較早時為搵食走出馬路被撞斃，正調查意外經過。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181217/bkn-20181217064110479-1217_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181217%2Fbkn-20181217064110479-1217_00822_001.html&d=t%2F78%2BODoCXm3BL3z0AU5Bf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a52dfe2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181217/bkn-20181217064110479-1217_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"552b8957511e88057fd11a362bedc794bfb51c85","tid":944114,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:17:27.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0111f1362a1e0149e06c422ced919a13418ed8a","tid":944114,"uid":3691,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"53906c1c0c72e37546129a63f17b781892b2f3ac","tid":944114,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181217/photo/bkn-2018121706411047